Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Spike is great\NMaking a jewel cake{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.50,0:00:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, that's who.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Been saving up my gems\NSo fine{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For a cake\NThat is divine{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.20,0:00:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you "hooing" at?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. They're delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you see them,\Nnow you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.26,0:00:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is how you make\NA jewel cake{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.68,0:00:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stir in some gems\NAnd then you bake{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gonna eat, eat, eat it up\NGonna--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.77,0:00:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened\Nto all my jewels?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a bowl full of them here\Nand now I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.70,0:01:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means,\Nsomebody took them!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.76,0:01:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who? That's what I'm asking.\NWho?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.25,0:01:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Who took my jewels?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.95,0:01:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm who.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.73,0:01:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This cake was gonna be\Nso good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.87,0:01:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Whyyyyyyyyy??!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.14,0:01:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Season 3 | Episode 11\NJust for Sidekicks
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Subbed by GrayJeager\NFr.Jeager@gmail.com
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.96,0:02:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,http://www.youtube.com/user/GrayJeager3\Nhttp://www.youtube.com/user/GhxBronie\Nhttp://grayjeager.blogspot.fr (french)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no jewels{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no cake{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.67,0:02:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm a sad little dragon\NWith nothing to--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Oh goodness, I hope\NI'm not interrupting anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I do have this cake\Nto not bake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. It's a bad time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside joke, talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that Princess Cadence\Nneeds us to do a great job
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.15,0:02:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,welcoming the head\Nof the Equestria games
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,when she visits\Nthe Crystal Empire tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know all about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I wouldn't be any help\Nat welcoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know\Nwhat I was thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, you might be upset\Nfor not being invited,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and here I am coming to ask you\Nfor a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You were probably\Ngoing to say no, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:03:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All I had to offer you in exchange\Nwas one little jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.60,0:03:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All I have is this jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a really big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A really big, juicy,\Nperfect for a cake-topper jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.62,0:03:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean you'll do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.35,0:03:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you. Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So while I'm gone,\Nyou'll take care of Angel,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and tomorrow is Tuesday,\Nwhich is his tail fluffing day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's really important\Nfor him to look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what? You want me\Nto take care of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it's too much\Ntrouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can always see\Nif there's somepony else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We already agreed on the\Nwhole jewel thing, so I'll just--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you,\Nthank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel, aren't you\Njust so excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:04:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, she's not\Nthe only pony with a pet
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that might need\Nsome watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.70,0:04:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All I'm saying is if Fluttershy thought\Nthat her beloved little friend
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,shouldn't be left alone while\Nyou're busy in the Crystal Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,then maybe that's just\Nsomething to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tank's not some fuzzy\Nlittle bunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He can take care of himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a strong, fearless\Nand totally together pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, you can watch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:04:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But only because, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tank's got a strict\Nflying regimen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and someone needs to make sure\Nthat he doesn't slack off while I'm gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the two of us\Nare very diligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. And more importantly,\Nas for Opal,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,she likes to eat every\N36 and a half minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You groom her with\Nher silken brush, head to toe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't forget to pooch\Nher pillow out in the middle,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that's where she likes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And the temperature in the room\Nshould always be exactly 81.4 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only way\Nshe can get to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So thanks for your help\Nand good luck to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the dragon was expecting\Na little something for his efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost as beautiful\Nas the pony who gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you be critter-proofing\Nthe library or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:05:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Tank has a tendency to--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Critter-proofing.\NYeah, I'll get right on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Three down, three to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that you said, Gummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're just gonna have\Nto ask Pinkie Pie about that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask me! Ask me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course,\Nyou can have another cupcake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Why didn't you say so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you a bigger pond\Nimmediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think what Gummy's\Ntrying to say is--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always wanted a pair\Nof riding pants?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.26,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,His toenails need\Na new coat of shellack?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to floss twice a day\Ninstead of just once?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I think what Gummy is trying to say\Nis that he'd like a little Spike time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wouldn't?\NSpike time is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Alas, it doesn't come cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:07:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All I'm saying is that you might\Nwanna think about a helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You only wanna get hit in the head\Nby a flying turtle... once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A thousand plus carats\Nof pure deliciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you got a regular\Npet day care in here, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll still be able to get\Nsome good playtime
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,with Winona like you said,\Nthough, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She tends to get a little wild\Nif she doesn't get her exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Exercise, sure, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember seeing\Ncritters on the invite list.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because we're leaving\Nthem here with Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gonna do a little\Ncritter sitting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.75,0:07:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry I'm late.\NSilly bunny had hidden his brush.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure you get plenty\Non his tail
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,or it won't get as poofy\Nas he likes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, girls,\Nor we're gonna miss the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,One more for the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you little puppy,\Ncome on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I love you more!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:07:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you more!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I promise\Nit will be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fluff your tail\Ntwice next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Three times?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know, it's a chilly\N81.2 in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, take care of this,\Nwould you please?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.15,0:08:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what're you thinking about\Nthat hooting little friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Suppose you'll want me\Nto keep an eye on him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you don't already\Nhave your hands full?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But, just between you and me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta give priority\Nto the paying customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely sure\Nyou can do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! Wouldn't have\Nagreed to it if I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Piece of cake.\NSpeaking of cake,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a little something\NI need to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like, keeping an eye\Non a house full of critters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah. That was totally\Nwhat I was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax! Go to your welcoming\Nthing in the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike's got it all under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, sidekicks!\NFront and center!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There are six of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's only one\Nright here in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Two. And what I say goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.41,0:09:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, the boss of you,\Nthat's who.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, number four.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.79,0:10:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All I wanted were some jewels.\NBig, juicy delicious jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And now what do I have?\NA missing rabbit and--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, little fluffy Angel Bunnykins,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.26,0:10:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The natural waves in his fluff\Nare to die for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Angel just the cutest thing\Nyou've ever seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, you don't wanna\Nbe with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather not chase you around\Nall over the place
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,when I could be enjoying\Nsome jewel cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch me solve\Nboth our problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:11:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm supposed to be\Nwatching him,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but you all have just hit it off\Nso well, that maybe--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I could let you\Ntake care of him instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We would, but we've got some major\NCrusaders business planned for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Major. We're getting our\Nskydiving Cutie Marks today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose\Nif you've got other plans...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just--\NYou're so good with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Like "get a Cutie Mark\Nfor bunny-sitting" good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A bunny-sitting Cutie Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He does seem to like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And we hadn't exactly\Nfigured out
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,how we're going to pull off\Nthis whole skydiving thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.81,0:11:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,As hard as it's gonna be for me\Nto part with these little guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you should probably\Njust take all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ask me, the more critters\Nyou take care of,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the more chances you have of getting\Nsome kind of critter-sitting Cutie Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I right?\NOr am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes!\N- But wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we gonna take good\Ncare of them
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,without treats\Nfor when they're good?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.65,0:12:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll need beds\Nfor when their tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And toys.\NThey need toys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't need all that stuff.\NThey'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to be able\Nto buy them some things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.55,0:12:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,One jewel might be able\Nto cover it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.76,0:12:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What would I possibly\Nbe doing with jewels?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I happen to know for a fact
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that Applejack gave you a gem\Nto watch Winona.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.53,0:12:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously no one around here\Nis getting a Cutie Mark
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,for kindness towards a poor,\Nhungry little dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it or leave it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gonna put in some flour\NAnd add a little sugar{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For my five\NDelicious jewels{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But pink feathers would look\Nso good with your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That bird could use\Na little color.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Has anyone seen Tank's head?\NWhere's his head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:13:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What've you done\Nto the turtle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he totally forgot\Nhe could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. So pretty sure\Ncritter-sitting Cutie Marks are out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And our critter-grooming\NCutie Marks
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,probably aren't going to appear\Nany time soon either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All right,\Nload them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can give me back\Nthat jewel I gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.\NWe don't have it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you think we paid\Nfor the industrial-sized pet hair dryer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Zecora knows just what to do
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,about all this bad mojo\Nthat's floating around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking a cage\Nand a great big lock might be next.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.34,0:14:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Zecora can take the bad away\Nif you do just what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But before I can do my duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.75,0:14:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to need\Nsome of your booty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You think jewels\Nare what you need,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's no worse mojo\Nthan dragon greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just taking good care\Nof everyone's animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna have to do\Nto get this to go away?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this is just\Nbetween you and me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No other pony\Nhas to hear a word about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A word about what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This better be important.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.51,0:15:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't have all of these\Nanimals on my train.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Not without tickets\Nand not without chaperones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All I need is to get\Non for one minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,grab a bunny and get off!\NPromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A likely story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No chaperone, no train!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Skydiving Cutie Marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is three ponies enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,At least I have you two left,\Nmy delectable little treasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All aboard\Nfor the Crystal Empire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.91,0:16:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Crystal Empire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to see\Nthe Crystal Empire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I were dressed for it,\Nbut still... the Crystal Empire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not really going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.26,0:16:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We just needed to get on the train\Nso I can get that rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.56,0:16:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I do, we're off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.68,0:16:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?\N- It's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Next stop, the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.92,0:16:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So it seems the Crystal Empire
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,would be really cold,\Nbut I've heard that it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as warm as can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think the walls are crystal?\NMaybe even see-through?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you imagine?\NSee-through walls!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it. Just take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, enjoy it while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not getting out of this car\Nuntil we're back in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way, no how,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.48,0:17:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,we're coming all the way\Nto the Crystal Empire
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.09,0:17:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,without looking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No pony's gonna get past\Nthis dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.96,0:17:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa. Just whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.63,0:18:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in crystal heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh. Quiet there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the bunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, please. Pretty please,\Ndon't go down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fluff your tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll perm, highlight and blow it out\Nif you'll just stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?\NName it, and it's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Without seeing the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this car's empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming this way.\NEverybody down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There has got to be\Na better solution!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sit down,\Ndon't sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.26,0:19:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My dogs are barking!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.86,0:19:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Did y'all hear that?\NThey really are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Bummer, Spike got\Nto miss out on all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He would have had fun here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.56,0:19:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he's havinga great time\Nwatching all the critters back at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Think he's still got a handle\Non things?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If he is staying calm\Nand collected,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet he is doing\Na terrific job as a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, bunny.\NDo your worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.00,0:19:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.89,0:19:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I ignored you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.48,0:19:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,tried to pawn you off\Non someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't take these silly things out\Nor fluff this like I was supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't really thinking\Nabout you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Any of you.\NJust wanted the jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll all forgive me\Nsomeday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.99,0:19:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You will?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the one\Nwho gives us away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.78,0:20:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you--?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You all hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.94,0:20:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to scratch\Nthe belly on Winona!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I miss her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.43,0:20:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait\Nto see Owlowicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thought we'd meet you\Nat the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So we could hear all about\Nthe Crystal Empire
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.06,0:20:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and find out if you brought us\None of the Crystal snow globes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that they sell\Nat the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know\Nabout the snow globes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta hand it to you,\NSpike.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.39,0:20:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You did a really good job\Nof taking care of the animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spike,\NAngel looks perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You did such a good job\Nfluffing his tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well,\Nwe're like this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You know who.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.51,0:21:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what are you thinking?\NBake them into a jewel pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Six-layer gem cake\Nsounds pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.77,0:21:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It really, really does.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Whyyyyyyyy??!
